org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2

Interface IMessage<ParameterType>

  • Type Parameters:
    ParameterType - Template parameter which defines the type of the given event's parameter.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringMessage

    public interface IMessage<ParameterType>
    Interface that defines the base functions of the parametric messages being sent between individual ITransformationStep objects. These messages have a parameter defined by the template parameter. These messages are not used for transferring control from one step to another, only for data transfer.
